title.narrative: Procurement and logistics for equipment and medical supplies for Treatment Centres - RDEL

description.narrative: This activity (Procurement and logistics for equipment and medical supplies for Treatment Centres - RDEL) is a component of Ebola Treatment Centres in Sierra Leone reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £22,474,446. This component benefits Sierra Leone, and works in the following sector(s): Material relief assistance and services . , with the following implementing partners: British High Commission, Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 11-10-2014 and the end date is 31-08-2015.
